een more skeptical of the whistleblower=E2=80=99s accusation that Amin was =
overseeing =E2=80=9Cmass hysterectomies,=E2=80=9D given that the network fo=
und evidence of only two. The judge also noted that Hayes, for one, =E2=80=
=9Cdiscounted the whole thing=E2=80=9D before he went on national televisio=
n and compared the situation to Nazi Germany or the Jim Crow South. Indeed,=
 the judge added, NBC=E2=80=99s actions might rise to actual malice. On the=
 other hand, in the <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZ=
CI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dRZGxJVHFHWGhLOWg5Z0NaS0ZQYz0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0=
cHM6Ly93d3cuZG9jdW1lbnRjbG91ZC5vcmcvZG9jdW1lbnRzLzI0Nzg2MDQwLWFtaW4_dXRtX2N=
