ld" class=3D"sdf">the one</a></u> 15 years ago when California attempted to=
 restrict the sale of violent video games to minors.<br/><br/>Amicus briefs
are also valuable when the case=E2=80=99s primary party lacks widespread sy=
mpathy. While few may empathize with ByteDance and its Chinese government p=
